## Notes: |cFFFF0000Version 2.1.0|r - Major feature update with game record editing system! Challenge your target, track your stats, edit your history, and let fate decide! |n|n|cffffffffNew in v2.1:|r|n- |cff00ff00Game Record Editing System|r - Fix mistakes in wager amounts, results, and rolls|n- |cff00ff00Color-coded History|r - Green for wins, red for losses in edit dialogs|n- |cff00ff00Data Management Tab|r - Organized settings for all data operations|n- |cff00ff00Enhanced Display|r - Proper "You vs Opponent" format throughout|n- |cff00ff00Critical Bug Fixes|r - Settings now work properly, post-duel challenges fixed|n|n|cffffffffCore Features:|r|n- Professional AceGUI interface with modern styling|n- |cffffff00Edit game records|r after completion via /dr edit command|n- Detailed win/loss history tracking per player (limited to recent 5 games)|n- Advanced gold tracking with streaks and statistics|n- Smart minimap integration with LibDBIcon|n- Automatic emote reactions on wins/losses|n- Cross-version compatibility (Classic Era, TBC, Wrath, Cata, Retail)|n- Professional options panel with organized data management|n- Data export/import functionality|n|n|cffffffffCommands:|r|n- |cffffff00/dr or /deathroll:|r Open the main DeathRoll window|n- |cff00ff00/dr config:|r Open configuration options|n- |cffff8800/dr edit:|r Edit recent game records|n- |cff82c5ff/drh [player]:|r View history with specific player|n|n|cffbbbbbbBy EgyptianSheikh - Enhanced with game editing features|r
